    <item>
      <title>卡车司机工会主席将在共和党全国代表大会上发表讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/teamsters-president-to-speak-at-republican-national-convention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布，卡车司机工会主席肖恩·奥布莱恩将于下个月在密尔沃基举行的共和党全国代表大会上发表讲话，此举可能会削弱总统乔·拜登对蓝领工会工人的吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/teamsters-president-to-speak-at-republican-national-convention</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部表示尚未决定是否起诉波音</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/doj-says-it-still-hasn-t-decided-whether-to-prosecute-boeing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部告诉两起 737 Max 致命坠机事故受害者家属的律师，在上个月确定波音公司违反了与政府达成的 2021 年协议后，仍未决定是否对波音公司提起刑事指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/doj-says-it-still-hasn-t-decided-whether-to-prosecute-boeing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:18:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉在维持利率不变后抨击央行行长为“对手”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/lula-blasts-central-bank-chief-as-adversary-after-rate-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦称央行行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托是“政治和意识形态的对手”，在政策制定者本周停止为期一年的宽松周期后，他对货币当局的批评进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/lula-blasts-central-bank-chief-as-adversary-after-rate-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:06:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加密货币赠款超额后，文克莱沃斯兄弟获得退款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/winklevoss-twins-refunded-after-trump-crypto-gift-exceeded-limit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡梅伦·文克莱沃斯和泰勒·文克莱沃斯向唐纳德·特朗普总统竞选活动捐赠的比特币超过了联邦法律允许的最高金额，因此他们获得了退款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/winklevoss-twins-refunded-after-trump-crypto-gift-exceeded-limit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 19:05:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国改革派领袖法拉奇称北约和欧盟“挑起”了乌克兰战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/nato-and-eu-to-blame-for-ukraine-war-reform-uk-s-farage-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国民粹主义改革党领袖奈杰尔·法拉奇认为，北约和欧盟向东欧扩张是俄罗斯入侵乌克兰的罪魁祸首。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/nato-and-eu-to-blame-for-ukraine-war-reform-uk-s-farage-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普进军 2024 年大选 哈里斯向华尔街高层示好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/wall-street-brass-courted-by-harris-as-trump-makes-2024-inroads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯正在与美国企业高层培养关系，向那些有迹象表明将在 11 月大选中大力支持共和党人唐纳德·特朗普的团体伸出了橄榄枝。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/wall-street-brass-courted-by-harris-as-trump-makes-2024-inroads</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 17:45:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国相对于德国的风险溢价达到 2012 年以来的最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-s-risk-premium-over-germany-closes-at-highest-since-2012</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心，争夺法国即将到来的立法选举的政党可能会进一步导致公共财政膨胀，投资者对法国债券的持有要求比对更安全的德国债券的持有要求高出十多年来的最大溢价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/france-s-risk-premium-over-germany-closes-at-highest-since-2012</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 16:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度教徒因在日内瓦别墅剥削仆人被判有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/hindujas-found-guilty-of-exploitation-of-servants-at-swiss-villa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁欣杜贾家族的四名成员因在日内瓦别墅中剥削低薪仆人而被判有罪，这一判决对印度最富有和最有影响力的家族之一的瑞士分支来说是毁灭性的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/hindujas-found-guilty-of-exploitation-of-servants-at-swiss-villa</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 15:38:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党获得的大额捐款比英国保守党多 14 倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/labour-and-reform-lead-uk-conservatives-on-campaign-donations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国大选竞选活动的第二周，英国工党反对派获得的大额捐款至少是首相里希·苏纳克领导的保守党的 14 倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/labour-and-reform-lead-uk-conservatives-on-campaign-donations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 14:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国或将效仿苏纳克的庇护计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/germany-weighs-copying-uk-asylum-plan-as-scholz-faces-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府承认，邻国大力宣传的移民计划并没有取得很好的效果。但由于这一问题暴露了其关键的政治弱点，德国政府仍准备继续推进，以抵御随时准备发起攻击的右翼势力的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/germany-weighs-copying-uk-asylum-plan-as-scholz-faces-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 22:00:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
